Text: A woman won a travel to portugal, she is not sure of going so finally she de
  decides to stay and keep working where she is being the last yesr of her life. Accepting
  that travel would mean have to quit and lose the stability she loves. But to win
  that travel makes her think that maybr is the moment of making a changes. Before
  the day with the deadline to accept the prize she discovers that her boyfriend is
  cheating on her with one of her old friends. After that she starting making her
  luggage and ready to know what portugal have ready for her.
